summary: I am a multilingual (English, Portuguese, Spanish) Italian-Brazilian professional with extensive experience working for international companies, having opened and managed my own companies and coordinated United Nations projects in Brazil. A Master's degree in Social Sciences and an MBA in International Business gave me the ability to better understand how cultural differences can impact international business and how businesses today should pursue a more sustainable development. Now, I am having a blast at FareHarbor in Amsterdam!
